            'Method 1: Calculate power then mod',
            '7³ = 343',
            '343 ÷ 5 = 68 remainder 3',
            '7³ mod 5 = 3',
            'Method 2: Reduce at each step (efficient for large powers)',
            '7 mod 5 = 2',
            '(7²) mod 5 = (2²) mod 5 = 4',
