        type: 'rational_expressions',
        subparts: [
            'Given: 2/(x+1) + 3/(x-2)',
            'Find common denominator: (x+1)(x-2)',
            'Rewrite first fraction:',
            '2/(x+1) = 2(x-2)/[(x+1)(x-2)]',
            'Rewrite second fraction:',
            '3/(x-2) = 3(x+1)/[(x+1)(x-2)]',
            'Add numerators:',
            '= [2(x-2) + 3(x+1)] / [(x+1)(x-2)]',
            'Expand numerator:',
            '= [2x - 4 + 3x + 3] / [(x+1)(x-2)]',
            '= (5x - 1) / [(x+1)(x-2)]',
            'Answer: (5x-1)/[(x+1)(x-2)]',
            'Restrictions: x ≠ -1, x ≠ 2'
        ],
        helper: 'Find LCD, rewrite with common denominator, add numerators',
