            'Take ln: ln(1.312525) = n × ln(1.004167)',
            'n = ln(1.312525)/ln(1.004167)',
            'n ≈ 0.272/0.004158',
            'n ≈ 65.4 months',
            'Answer: About 66 months (5.5 years)',
            'Need to deposit for about 5 years and 6 months'
